data.meta_description:
78 likes, 0 comments - theherocollect on April 3, 2024: "Poster Showcase: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire (2024)

‘Rise together of Fall alone!’

“Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire” is a 2024 American monster film directed by Adam Wingard. Produced by Legendary Pictures, it is a sequel to “Godzilla vs. Kong” (2021), and the fifth film in the “MonsterVerse franchise”.

Did You Know…It is also the 38th film of the Godzilla franchise and the 13th film in the King Kong franchise?
